00:00:03.680 --> 00:00:05.670
by the graphs of f
of x is equal to 8x

00:00:05.670 --> 00:00:08.830
to the third and g of x
is equal to sine of pi x,

00:00:08.830 --> 00:00:10.052
as shown in the figure above.

00:00:10.052 --> 00:00:11.760
And they drew the
